description:
On this week’s mini-episode, Kate and Doree offer advice on how to get your partner to commit to couple’s therapy and tips on grappling with imposter syndrome. Plus, they answer a listener question on how to look fresh and put together even when you’re exhausted.

To leave a voicemail for a future episode, call 781-591-0390. To learn more, visit forever35podcast.com.
